This ultrasoft pseudopotential has been generated in the
Mn 2+ configuration (3d4.5 4s0.4 4p0.1), with uspp-7.3.6,
and converted to UPF. This pseudopotential has been tested
succesfully on simple solids (Mn-fcc, MnO) as well as on
some Mn organic complexes, by D. Ceresoli and E. Li.

